Bashir El-Rufai, one of the sons of Kaduna Governor and his wife have welcomed twin boys. According to Bashir, his wife and babies are in good health condition.   Clash on Lagos Island: We have made some arrests –…     Nothing can make me return to party politics –…     Please pray for my health, Olisa Metuh begs Nigerians   Bashir wedded Halima Kazaure, daughter of former Jigawa Senator Ibrahim Kazaure on November 21, 2020 in Abuja. The wedding was attended by many dignitaries including Senate President, Ahmad Lawan; former emir of Kano Muhammadu Sanusi II; Jigawa Governor Badaru Abubakar; Yobe State Governor Mai Mala Buni and others. “Alhamdulillah. My wife just gave birth to beautiful identical twin boys. Mother is doing great. Father is ecstatic. Thank you Allah. It was all you,” Bashir tweeted.